# Next.js Patterns

- Default to **Server Components**; add `'use client'` only for hooks, browser APIs, or local state.
- Colocate `loading.tsx`, `error.tsx`, and `not-found.tsx` for catalog and CRM sections.
- Fetch in server components via services; pass serializable props to clients.

```tsx
// GOOD: server page, client cart button only
export default async function ProductPage({ params }: { params: { slug: string } }) {
  const product = await productService.getBySlug(params.slug);
  return (
    <>
      <ProductDetails product={product} />
      <AddToCartButton productId={product.id} />
    </>
  );
}
```

- Use `generateMetadata` for SEO (team name, bat model) with es-MX titles.
- Route groups: `(storefront)`, `(crm)`, `(auth)` - keep CRM behind middleware auth.
